#: includes/eme-options.php:1791
msgid "When a person that is not logged-in wants to look at a private event, that person is redirected to the WordPress login page. If you want to redirect to another url, enter it here. The permalink of the current visited page will be added to the mentioned url query string with a parameter called \"redirect\"."
