#: includes/eme-options.php:2483
msgid "Should contain at least the placeholder #_SUB_CONFIRM_URL (if this placeholder is not present, people will not be able to confirm their subscription). Next to that, #_LASTNAME and #_FIRSTNAME can also be used. You should also advise the person that this subscription confirmation link is only valid for a specific amount of time (typically one day)."
